						<summary>

						<p>On a rock near a tank called Abbināyanicheruvu.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Nandana, Āshāḍha, ba. 5.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register the grant of the <hi rend="italic">gauḍika</hi> right to a certain Channamareḍḍi of Vēlaguṇṭla by Immaḍi Chikkarāya Tammaya Gavunivāru.</p>						

